    "Finally, 18 diseases belonging to 10 plant species are selected as research objects to construct the dataset, for example, common plants such as apples, pears, and tomatoes. 2.",
    "Image collection: Images are collected in a variety of ways, such as search engine downloads, web crawling, and manual collection.",
    "The image collection is mainly based on web crawling and search engine downloads, supplemented by manual collection.",
    "In the end, more than 50,000 candidate images are collected.",
    "At the same time, the collection of images complies with relevant regulations such as copyright and privacy. 3."
